{"tid":513514,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你 港女會唔會太玻璃心","createTime":"2017-12-29T15:05:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T00:58:09.000Z","uid":62121,"like":30,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"153d1922081677532900a8f237b7fbe0ca2d41f6","tid":513514,"uid":62121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T15:05:39.000Z","msg":"是咁的 早幾日有三條港女(仲要生得醜既)入黎我地鋪頭<br />\n因為d名店都會有好多保安行來行去.. <br />\n<br />\n然後港女A同港女B講：「我唔明佢做乜要跟住我囉！」<br />\n港女B：「咪係！係覺得我會偷野定點呀？」<br />\n（利申番 平時啲保安哥哥懶過鬼  完全唔會有興致跟住啲客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n港女C：「係囉！好唔尊重我地囉！」<br />\n<br />\n以為事情就咁完啦，點知呢三條港女行左去搵人投訴，<br />\n投訴呢個保安員跟住佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁搵左兩個同事安撫完佢地都唔撚順超，話要攞番個公道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拍哂檯 揮哂手話要搵經理，<br />\n<br />\n又話乜不被尊重，又話乜只係想攞番個公道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲迫個保安哥哥道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n經理都解釋番 話保安只係職責所在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n港女仲大大聲：「唔洗道歉 益左佢啦！」<br />\n<br />\n之後我就唔知點了..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad6af6ecdd9ed3d500d0ad6aee054982f62e161","tid":513514,"uid":6017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T15:44:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd8109f3a61bb565599e3c4f8f30cc1a855e2fd2","tid":513514,"uid":78429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T15:46:15.000Z","msg":"醜就算啦, 佢地都唔想"},{"pid":"fa4029bee52e94bbc11b56f8a5c9baff59209f20","tid":513514,"uid":116705,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score